                             Our Coverage Area
                        </span>
                        <h2 class="cs-title">Where We Work in Southern New Mexico</h2>
                        <p class="cs-text">Brainard's Greenscapes serves homeowners and businesses across the greater Las Cruces area and southern Doña Ana County. Our crews are based right here in Las Cruces. We travel throughout the Mesilla Valley, up into the Organ Mountain foothills, and south to towns near the New Mexico-Texas border. That covers about 30 miles in every direction from downtown.</p>
                        <p class="cs-text">We work in neighborhoods like Sonoma Ranch and Picacho Hills, historic towns like Mesilla and Doña Ana, and the growing foothill areas of Talavera, Soledad Canyon, and Dripping Springs. No matter what kind of soil or terrain your property has, we have worked on land just like it.</p>
                        <p class="cs-text">Every landscape we build is made for the desert. That means tough soils, only about 10 inches of rain per year, heavy monsoon storms, and extreme summer heat. We also know the local watering rules from Las Cruces Utilities and the permit process for the City and County. If your neighborhood has HOA rules, we know how to work with those too. All of this local know-how means fewer surprises, faster work, and a landscape that lasts.</p>
                    </div>
